                 <l n="c">Ākṣeptā cānumantā ca</l>
                 <l n="d">dvayam eva narakaṁ v<surplus>r</surplus>a<lb n="51" break="no"/><supplied reason="omitted">se</supplied>T<g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></l><!-- 
