                   <l n="b">bhūr vaiṣṇavī sūrya-sut<choice><sic>a</sic><corr>ā</corr></choice>ś ca gāvaḥ<g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></l>
                   <l n="c">yaḥ
                       <pb n="3r"/><lb n="52"/> kāñcanaṁ gāñ ca mahīñ ca dadyād</l>
